aces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4a76585ad7603353aba3984639c266da806d822d","tid":1630951,"uid":27112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"佢講嘅神明係咪指佢自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcadda6be248e7ad030074acd4cf239ecaf61ca","tid":1630951,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f486ed200c0abb8bebf17c5ee968e175e8be523f","tid":1630951,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98bb5b0a6bcb6321ebdde88c8eef9f63f7f4009a","tid":1630951,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:28:19.000Z","msg":"好似有首正啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:35:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KaDrixwOy9g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKaDrixwOy9g&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6sVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%